Dino Melaye, a senator Kogi West has emerged as the campaign spokesperson of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) in the 2019 election.  He announced this via his Twitter handle on Friday. Thank you PDP for my appointment as Director incharge of Civil Societies/ NGO'S and Campaign Spokesperson in the PDP Presidential Campaign. We shall usually overcome. Light will always rejoice over darkness. Power to the People.- SDM — Senator Dino Melaye (@dino_melaye) November 30, 2018    He said: “Thank you PDP for my appointment as Director incharge of Civil Societies/ NGO’S and Campaign Spokesperson in the PDP Presidential Campaign. We shall usually overcome. Light will always rejoice over darkness. Power to the People.- SDM”